            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>flaked almonds </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your<strong> ground turmeric </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) to the<strong> food processor</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Pulse until you're left with a slightly chunky paste – this is your<strong> Malaysian-style spice paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1-1636107485348-x200.jpg",
