            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle, then heat a large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> to the pan and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through and starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
