        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Malaysian-style spice paste</strong> to the<strong> </strong>meat-free chick'n and cook for 2-3<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant,<strong> </strong>add your<strong> tamarind paste</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and cook for a further 2-3 min</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!), then add it to the pan and cook for 1 min further – this is your <strong>Malaysian-style coconut meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
