      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Malaysian-style coconut meat-free chick'n</strong> with the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
